<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org" lang="en">

<head th:replace="~{fragments :: head('Home | My Website')}">
	<link rel="stylesheet" th:href="@{/css/style.css}">
	<link rel="stylesheet" th:href="@{/css/style.css}">
</head>

<body class="bg-light">
    <nav th:replace="~{fragments :: navbar}"></nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <h2 class="mb-4 pb-2 border-bottom">Latest Articles</h2>
                
                <div th:each="post : ${posts}" class="card mb-4 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title fw-bold" th:text="${post.title}">Title</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3" th:text="${#temporals.format(post.createdAt, 'MMMM dd, yyyy')}">Date</p>
                        <p class="card-text" th:text="${#strings.abbreviate(post.content, 150)}">Content...</p>
                        <a th:href="@{/post/{id}(id=${post.id})}" class="text-primary text-decoration-none fw-bold">Read More &rarr;</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold">About Me</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted small">
                        	Hey and welcome to my page! My name is Rumen and I love science, more specifically
                        	maths, computer science, AI, embedded systems, Robotics and Cybersecurity. In my free time I love to skateboard,
                        	spend time with friends and creating stuff. I love to challenge myself with hard maths problems and riddles. I am intereted in 
                        	wide variety of topics. If you want to collaborate, don't hesitate to reach out to me:
                        </p>
                        
                        <ul>
                        	<li>My email: rumenstvass@gmail.com</li>
                        </ul>
                      
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>